description.en: 1Swap is the first stablecoin-DEX project on Moonriver Network. Our main product is 1Swap, a decentralized stablecoin exchange which allows users to efficiently swap stablecoins and pegged assets. The 1Swap AMM offers low slippage and just 0.04% swap fees which results to the best swap rates. With all main and popular stablecoins listed already, we are the premier place for MOVRines to swap their stable assets!
